WEBVTT

00:00.100 --> 00:01.439
Previously on The O.C....

00:01.440 --> 00:03.814
Your mother has a drinking problem. She needs help.

00:03.815 --> 00:05.362
Mom, please, you got to do this.

00:05.363 --> 00:07.556
Who knew my new Playstation idol would be your new girl...

00:07.557 --> 00:08.661
- Your new...
- Friend.

00:08.662 --> 00:10.473
I would love to go to Cabo with you.

00:10.614 --> 00:11.213
Cabo?

00:11.214 --> 00:12.504
I know about you and my dad.

00:12.505 --> 00:16.403
My dad just got out of a marriage, and I don't want him rushing back into another.

00:16.404 --> 00:18.570
Right now, the board is watching you, waiting for you to screw up,

00:18.572 --> 00:20.252
and you're screwing up.

00:20.251 --> 00:23.216
What's it going to be, hospital or Matt?

00:23.213 --> 00:24.679
You and Marissa going to be okay at the house?

00:24.672 --> 00:26.344
Oh, yeah, of course.

